metadata.name: I Revel In My Element. #1/20
metadata.description:
What is mastery?, you may think it’s getting to the peak of your abilities  
But to me it’s a lot more than that, it’s a revelation of potential.

Rooted in mastery is the potential to do more, to become more,  
To strike a point where exponential growth is inevitable and your will to become is unstoppable.

This is my Element, and I Revel in it.

AnjolaDave.✦  
2022
